      "content": "i know about seeking help but it feels like a bandaid on a bullet wound. it's not just a \"bad day,\" it's the realization that the world is fundamentally built to reject me. it feels like there's no actual way to win. everything i do to be myself just feels like more friction. i'm just exhausted from the constant damage it does to my soul. it feels so pointless. like why bother even trying to fix something that's just broken by design?",
